name: SAMSIA RURAL HEALTH AND ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT SOCIETY
briefDescription: Our organization is working (2015-2016) on MKSP (Mahila Kishan Swashakti Pariyajana), 27 number sansads, covered 3000 Kishan families, Livelihood and Food Security among the poor and initiate capacity building among civil society and local government institutions, covered 1 Gram Panchayat, covered 15000 families, Water & sanitation program 3 Gram Panchayat, target families 12000 families, Anti trafficking, women empowerment, adolescent girls empowerment, education activities on cholo school e jai, PW Act-198, AIDs, Environment etc.
